Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.50,0:04:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们把β内腓肽编码提高3%吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.50,0:04:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【endorphin】：内腓肽，是一种脑下垂体分泌的类吗啡激素，有止痛和欣快感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.00,0:04:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谬小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.24,0:04:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,记者招待会上的发言要慎重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.97,0:04:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近窥探莎朗人工智能的记者很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.31,0:04:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.18,0:04:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.55,0:04:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.73,0:04:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脑波控制组件的同步率比上次提高了1.5%呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.97,0:04:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次把同步回路设定为DA-PLUS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.30,0:04:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK 是DA-PLUS吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.51,0:04:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,YF-19那边好像终于来替换的试飞员了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.51,0:04:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【YF-19 AVF原型试作机】:由新星重工（Shinsei Industry）\N研制的次期主力战斗机(AVF-Advanced Variable Fighter）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.34,0:04:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说是个破坏军纪的惯犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.15,0:05:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走到哪都会被调职
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.52,0:05:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他马上就要试飞了 要去看看吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.05,0:05:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管来的是谁 我都不会把计划拱手相让的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.01,0:06:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,控制塔呼叫雄鹰1号 我是米拉德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.11,0:06:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,YF-19和过去的机体不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.42,0:06:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请谨慎驾驶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.85,0:06:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了解 了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.21,0:06:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到达升限高度只要48秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.51,0:06:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【升限高度】：一架飞机上升时所能达到的极限高度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.81,0:06:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是不得了啊 小可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.05,0:06:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雄鹰1号 请回话 雄鹰1号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.25,0:06:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底在干什么 给我按测试计划表来飞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.13,0:06:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼 简直像无头苍蝇嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底在干什么啊 那个野蛮人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快看 第3追踪摄影机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.77,0:07:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.08,0:07:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么会是他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.30,0:08:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雄鹰1号 高速接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.96,0:08:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看你干了什么？我重要的YF-19可不是玩具…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.77,0:08:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐 刚才看到我的“龙鸟”了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.77,0:08:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【龙鸟】：行星伊甸上的特有生物，形似翼龙和鸟的结合体，背覆羽毛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.47,0:08:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可是我从天上送给你的礼物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.88,0:08:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这个野蛮人 听我说话的时候认真点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.80,0:08:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是不是很喜欢啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.45,0:08:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绘画时间结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.48,0:08:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么该到约会的时间了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.39,0:09:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去和米拉德上校约会吧\N好了 他在等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好小心点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.37,0:09:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是我们竞争对手的试飞员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.80,0:09:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伽尔德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.20,0:09:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也是试飞员？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.84,0:09:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这男的是个瘟神 会给周围的人带来不幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.21,0:09:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.28,0:09:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷静点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.85,0:09:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点去上校那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.85,0:09:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“做的太过火”是什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.56,0:09:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要把“挑战”和“莽撞”放在同一个口袋里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道是谁的名言吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.67,0:09:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.53,0:09:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我的名言 也是我得到的教训
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.24,0:09:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道自己的口袋里还有什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.94,0:09:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.78,0:09:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是愚蠢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.72,0:10:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是明白事理的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.46,0:10:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 开这么快很危险吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.57,0:10:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.44,0:10:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我可不想和你一起殉情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.08,0:10:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很惊心动魄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.72,0:10:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这个人还真怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.22,0:10:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.46,0:10:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这一带以前好像是森林
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.09,0:10:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过去在附近爬山的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.59,0:10:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看见了一只翼龙吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.59,0:10:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【Paleontology】：翼龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.73,0:10:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩 你知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.40,0:10:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个“达尔马提亚高中的可怜小子”就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.74,0:10:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌 你早点说嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.94,0:11:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那歌声？不…不是她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.25,0:11:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是莎朗的歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.25,0:11:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她很快就要来这里了 我很期待的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.28,0:11:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有点像我以前一个朋友的歌声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.32,0:11:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你肯定弄错了 莎朗可不是人类哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.99,0:11:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是人类？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.83,0:11:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了 管它呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.29,0:11:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位 多谢大家今天光临这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.90,0:12:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是“莎朗·艾普银河之旅”的总监制 谬芳容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.67,0:12:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎各位提问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.94,0:12:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说莎朗超越了自己虚拟偶像的身份\N现在被誉为“最受欢迎的大众情人”是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.05,0:12:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我老板雷蒙德还想收她作干女儿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.82,0:12:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但另一方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.19,0:12:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有些专家说没有感情的电脑歌声\N只不过是毒品而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.82,0:12:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有的事 她要是听到这种话会伤心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.26,0:12:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\an8}她的心思比人类还要细腻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.10,0:12:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.00,0:12:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,19那边看起来乱七八糟的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.53,0:12:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个乱画的驾驶员被罚3天内禁止登机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.24,0:12:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来胜利要属于我们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.24,0:12:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好别小看他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.81,0:12:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,军队里的大部分人都赌我们会赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.41,0:12:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是难以置信啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.58,0:12:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么各位 三天后\N我们在亚特兰提斯圆顶剧场再见吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.02,0:12:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天的记者招待会就到此为止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.56,0:13:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好像是从这个星球出生的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.92,0:13:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.30,0:13:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实你也想代替莎朗 用自己的嗓子来歌唱吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.57,0:13:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…我对唱歌已经没有留恋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.64,0:13:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎朗还是未完成品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.78,0:13:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,却已经俘虏了这么多人的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.68,0:13:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果哪天莎朗觉醒后想要单干的话\N我也就该退居二线了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.59,0:13:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要大家能得到感动 我就心满意足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.60,0:13:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是为什么她没有觉醒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.63,0:13:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,系统明明都完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.60,0:13:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道是…因为我的愿望不够强烈吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.11,0:13:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要太勉强自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.61,0:13:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,苦恼时的你也很美丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.45,0:13:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在已经很少见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.76,0:14:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过世的父亲以前常去深山里\N帮我摘这种名叫飞翔苹果的花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.30,0:14:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.77,0:14:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起 其实这是人造花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.59,0:15:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伽尔德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.46,0:15:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为什么…会在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.93,0:15:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在新闻里看到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.20,0:15:24.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然到了伊甸 我想你一定会来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.68,0:15:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你果然来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.98,0:15:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来的依然是个什么都没有的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.69,0:15:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么都没有的无聊地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.99,0:15:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你什么时候来伊甸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.79,0:15:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天刚到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.99,0:15:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,七年没回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.07,0:15:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道莎朗·艾普吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.24,0:16:00.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你对虚拟偶像什么的不感兴趣吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.94,0:16:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在是银河系NO.1歌手的监制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.58,0:16:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样 我很成功吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.98,0:16:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的歌呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.25,0:16:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很早以前就放弃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.39,0:16:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伽尔德你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.33,0:16:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是新型机的试飞员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.30,0:16:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在沙漠里的新爱德华兹基地工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.23,0:16:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你能飞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.70,0:16:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 这都是为了实现“在天空中自由飞翔”的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.51,0:16:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗 你也很努力呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.04,0:16:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 你也来听演唱会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.05,0:16:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能给你特等席哦 只需要滥用一下监制的职权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.42,0:16:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也刚做完演唱会的准备工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.72,0:16:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定会成为最精彩的演唱会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.39,0:16:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的 莎朗是最棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.73,0:17:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,够了 忘掉那时候说过的话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.21,0:17:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会让你忘记的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.26,0:17:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么嘛 有很多先来一步的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.40,0:17:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎？波曼主任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不见了 勇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.91,0:17:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.15,0:17:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你把我忘记了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.62,0:17:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是学院祭的偶像谬小姐吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.02,0:17:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到你变成伽尔德的女人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.04,0:18:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还是那么爱假装骑士啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.01,0:18:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这家伙 找上门来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.45,0:18:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.59,0:18:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亏你还有脸回伊甸来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.67,0:18:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会让给你的 不论谬还是计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.51,0:18:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手…住手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.71,0:18:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们两个像过去一样忘记我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.78,0:19:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在的我和你们认识的我不同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.40,0:19:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和那个时候不同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.08,0:19:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会让给你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.18,0:19:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,随你的便 但是计划我不会放弃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.38,0:19:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会让给你这种叛徒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.79,0:24:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心理反馈系统 运行良好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.79,0:24:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【MENTAL FEEDBACK SYSTERM】：\N将观众的心理活动通过手环传感器反馈到主机上\N以此来了解观众的口味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.33,0:24:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阈下情绪效应 已渗入潜在意识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.33,0:24:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【SUBLIMINAL EFFECT】：潜意识效应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.76,0:24:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,思想控制器切换至魅惑脉冲模式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.85,0:24:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脑波OS脉冲达到Level-3
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.48,0:25:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.92,0:25:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟你这个临时粉丝无关的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.02,0:25:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好看着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.33,0:25:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:30.31,0:25:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 发生了什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:31.88,0:25:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是程序错误？还是病毒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:50.00,0:25:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被人发现会被抓起来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:52.30,0:25:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没关系 因为她是MACROSS财团开发的最尖端人工智能系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:59.81,0:26:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,入侵不了她 我也就不配当“黑客宅男”了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:03.91,0:26:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自以为是的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:14.56,0:26:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:19.23,0:26:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了 你的心跳很混乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:18.72,0:27:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过来吧 莎朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:17.85,0:28:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个就是RF模块最后要更换的“扑克牌芯片”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:17.85,0:28:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【poker chip】：通指扑克筹码，一种赌博用的代币\N剧中应该是指像扑克一样薄的芯片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:24.75,0:28:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,简直像是“隐德来希”啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:24.75,0:28:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【entelechy】：亚里士多德提出的哲学词汇\N代表已达成目的、或将潜能变为现实的能动本源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:26.35,0:28:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不巧,我从来都没认同过亚里士多德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:30.59,0:28:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不相信他那句“灵魂与肉体是不可分离的”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:37.97,0:28:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是被你吓了一跳 谬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:40.23,0:28:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,居然看到你是莎朗·艾普的经纪人还是什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:43.80,0:28:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是监制哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:46.81,0:28:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了 是什么都好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:50.01,0:28:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凯特你还是老样子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:52.78,0:28:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经是两个孩子的母亲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:55.05,0:28:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你结婚了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:00.32,0:29:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你猜是跟谁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:02.82,0:29:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在勇、伽尔德和摩根之中的谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:06.36,0:29:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,摩根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:07.23,0:29:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真没劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:09.00,0:29:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶然见到过他们两个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:14.27,0:29:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们俩也都没变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:17.54,0:29:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像都在新爱德华兹基地做试飞员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:20.94,0:29:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗 大家都实现了各自的愿望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:25.75,0:29:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哟 好久不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:27.25,0:29:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,摩根
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:29.05,0:29:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么不叫我妈来照看孩子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:31.52,0:29:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然回家了一次…但是她们刚好在卖旧货
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:35.19,0:29:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果孩子们也被卖掉的话就麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:39.03,0:29:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是拿你没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:43.26,0:29:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:45.00,0:29:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上就开始模仿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:54.84,0:29:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊 好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:57.84,0:30:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么下一首就让谬唱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:01.32,0:30:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,期待很久了 学院祭的偶像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:05.79,0:30:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唱吧，就唱你以前作的那首歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:09.62,0:30:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是叫做“VOICES”吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:11.79,0:30:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:13.03,0:30:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:18.50,0:30:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…已经不唱歌了 都已经毕业了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:22.97,0:30:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且我已经厌倦了唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:25.74,0:30:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在哪还能记得住以前的歌啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:29.04,0:30:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:31.38,0:30:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么由我来唱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:35.68,0:30:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凯特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:38.05,0:30:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去解手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:47.56,0:30:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我 可以进去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:49.83,0:30:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我进来咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:57.77,0:31:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想问 “你究竟在做什么”对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:02.41,0:31:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我的“19”检修完毕之前\N我要诱拐莎朗小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:08.92,0:31:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 关键的部分就是出不来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:14.05,0:31:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然了 贞操可没那么容易到手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:17.99,0:31:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请不要把我和你混为一谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:20.53,0:31:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是在说感情程序的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:23.96,0:31:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我说…这东西也许有智能\N但它有心吗？心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:36.21,0:31:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇 你在那边吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:37.88,0:31:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是米拉德大叔找我 就说我不在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:40.85,0:31:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是女孩子打来的电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:42.58,0:31:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那接过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:46.09,0:31:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂喂？ 凯特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:49.09,0:31:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了 好久不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:50.32,0:31:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你居然知道我在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:53.06,0:31:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道你从高中开始就暗恋我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:56.56,0:31:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还是和以前一样笨啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:58.10,0:32:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又在墙上开洞了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:00.60,0:32:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的嘴巴还是那么毒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:03.10,0:32:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在我正和谬一起喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:07.31,0:32:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很奇怪啊 谬居然不唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:10.38,0:32:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说不再唱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:12.05,0:32:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她可是那个唱歌唱到废寝忘食\N连睡觉都不闲着的女人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:19.25,0:32:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做莎朗·艾普的监制一点也不适合她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:22.72,0:32:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,监制？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:24.12,0:32:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和那时候有关系吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:26.49,0:32:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是一直关系很好的你们\N忽然闹翻的那时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:32.13,0:32:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:33.87,0:32:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概因为大家都不是小鬼了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:37.07,0:32:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等下出来见个面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:38.71,0:32:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露个脸就好 让她打起精神来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:41.37,0:32:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别说笑了
