Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:08.82,1:00:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想让你留在我身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:11.16,1:00:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想让你一直留在我身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:15.49,1:00:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是为了保护你而活着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:19.06,1:00:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概从很久以前开始…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:28.04,1:00:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请收下这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:31.58,1:00:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我的护身符
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:33.61,1:00:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在下次见面之前 由你来保管它
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:37.95,1:00:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我现在还没…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:54.23,1:01:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一个词语是梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:02.44,1:01:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将我心中沉睡的黑暗悄悄带走
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:27.40,1:01:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二个词语是微风
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:35.71,1:01:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为我指引着方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:44.22,1:01:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我摆动翅膀飞向上帝的怀抱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:59.10,1:02:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,悲伤的往事随着时光流逝
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:14.55,1:02:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要突然做危险的动作
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:18.18,1:02:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在最终测试前如果再发生事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:21.55,1:02:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就开不了这种玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:23.05,1:02:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用担心 我的身体无论变成什么样都能修好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:27.79,1:02:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是说你 我担心的是机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:30.90,1:02:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:34.13,1:02:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:36.10,1:02:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下来 再去“疼爱”它一次好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:43.88,1:02:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:48.31,1:02:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么突然中止计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:51.45,1:02:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:54.39,1:02:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:56.09,1:02:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:57.42,1:02:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没法接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:58.59,1:03:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想犯侮辱长官罪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:00.56,1:03:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不管
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:01.43,1:03:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:02.69,1:03:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是统合军从总部发来的指令
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:05.00,1:03:06.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,指令？可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:06.70,1:03:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:11.24,1:03:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在地球秘密开发的无人战斗机已经完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:16.34,1:03:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无人战斗机？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:17.91,1:03:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听说军部选择了装有人工智能的GHOST-X9
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:24.78,1:03:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,军部指示要解除你们的一切职务
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:28.92,1:03:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是革职吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:30.42,1:03:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再也不需要驾驶员了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:33.36,1:03:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上校认为这样真的好吗 人类再也不能飞行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:38.13,1:03:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我一直以来所做的事有什么意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:42.37,1:03:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我耗费在YF-19上的青春该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:46.47,1:03:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去和将军理论
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:48.11,1:03:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让他见识下驾驶员的实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:49.81,1:03:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们给我适可而止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:54.45,1:03:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,军部已经决定在地球举行的宇宙大战\N终结纪念典礼上发表这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:59.42,1:04:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别再做丢人的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:02.59,1:04:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挑战结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:09.73,1:04:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:13.03,1:04:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为什么要道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:15.63,1:04:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她…谬小姐坐今早的宇宙航班回地球了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:22.71,1:04:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天有你的电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:25.64,1:04:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是她的朋友打来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:27.98,1:04:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没有告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:31.55,1:04:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:33.25,1:04:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道自己没那种权利
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:37.86,1:04:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一直都是自由之身
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:10.56,1:05:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我什么都没了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:19.57,1:05:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一条新闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:22.87,1:05:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新统合宇宙政府发起的30周年纪念典礼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:27.04,1:05:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全世界都像为莎朗而痴狂了一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:31.38,1:05:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做了什么特别宣传吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:36.45,1:05:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:38.15,1:05:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是理所当然的现象
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:40.99,1:05:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很快 梦想就会实现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:05.18,1:06:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:06.25,1:06:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都等得不耐烦了 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:09.18,1:06:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想闯入地球的典礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:10.92,1:06:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让GHOST大吃一惊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:15.02,1:06:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已经装好了超空间推进器
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:18.23,1:06:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会进入松弛睡眠状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:20.36,1:06:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在到达“地球绝对防御圈”之前 请你叫醒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:23.20,1:06:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 我能带着个小鬼去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:27.94,1:06:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果这种违反军纪的事暴露了 会被判处死刑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:31.71,1:06:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留下来我就会因为协助逃亡而被捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:35.31,1:06:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你会碍手碍脚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:37.11,1:06:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,YF-19不是你一个人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:46.55,1:06:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发生什么我都不管了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:03.00,1:07:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:03.77,1:07:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,YES SIR!
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:05.51,1:07:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了？是机库那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:19.39,1:07:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道 那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:22.92,1:07:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追击导弹正大量接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:24.63,1:07:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迎击吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:25.76,1:07:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪有时间理它
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:27.20,1:07:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用超空间航行摆脱它们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:27.20,1:07:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【FOLD】:利用重力使空间扭曲重叠\N并借此进行长距离移动的超空间航行法
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:28.66,1:07:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:29.70,1:07:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,距超空间航行系统启动还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:31.43,1:07:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5、4、3、2、1、0
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:43.44,1:07:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 已经进入超空间航行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:45.51,1:07:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通常战机不可能追上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:47.28,1:07:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能追击的只有YF-21
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:50.08,1:07:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我叫波曼出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:52.45,1:07:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是测试机由平民驾驶的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:54.79,1:07:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,责任由我来负
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:06.60,1:08:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会让你见谬的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:23.99,1:08:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,禁止入内是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:26.65,1:08:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是玛吉先生吩咐我们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:29.16,1:08:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让谬小姐你随便接近的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:30.99,1:08:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对莎朗造成负面影响就麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:34.16,1:08:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是说不再需要我了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:36.40,1:08:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:37.30,1:08:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,形式上有你在比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:40.17,1:08:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,形式上？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:41.80,1:08:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玛吉在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:43.30,1:08:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:45.61,1:08:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么随便解除谬的职务
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:48.38,1:08:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样莎朗怎么运作？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:52.78,1:08:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠生化神经芯片
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:52.78,1:08:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【BIO/NEURAL CHIP】：统合军秘密开发的芯片\N能使AI具有自动学习机能，疑似与ghost x-9搭载的芯片相同
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:55.22,1:08:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:56.45,1:08:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎朗已经有了自我学习的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:58.92,1:09:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不怕犯法吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:00.86,1:09:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那不是含有自我保存本能的可怕东西吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:04.19,1:09:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果那本能增幅该怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:06.09,1:09:07.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会产生无法预测的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:07.96,1:09:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那才是我们真正寻求的莎朗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:12.90,1:09:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你疯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:14.37,1:09:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能控制的话有什么用
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:17.37,1:09:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,演唱会要中止
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:19.07,1:09:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要立刻拆除芯片
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:34.82,1:09:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好 这里是主控室
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:38.33,1:09:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里很快就会变成一个\N没人在乎你死活的城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:43.80,1:09:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变成只能看到莎朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:45.50,1:09:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只能听到莎朗声音的城市
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:50.24,1:09:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切已开始向无法阻止的方向前进了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:38.55,1:10:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:53.47,1:10:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球人和杰特拉帝人携起手来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:04.21,1:11:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:05.35,1:11:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁来打开门
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:23.33,1:11:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人吗 谁来救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:26.67,1:11:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:42.35,1:11:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:57.06,1:11:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已经什么都不用做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:03.16,1:12:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你什么都做不到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:06.81,1:12:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:12.88,1:12:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:18.05,1:12:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是从你身上诞生出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:20.79,1:12:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是你的产物
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:25.29,1:12:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且现在 我已经与你不同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:31.33,1:12:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？你在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:40.61,1:12:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你喜欢伽尔德吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:45.11,1:12:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你更喜欢勇
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:49.98,1:12:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别说了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:56.09,1:12:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:05.86,1:14:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是自由的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:08.23,1:14:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自由？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:09.70,1:14:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我依靠自己的心灵活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:11.53,1:14:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不对 你是由程序设计出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:14.70,1:14:17.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你相信自己有感情也是虚构出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:19.11,1:14:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你真的拥有自己的意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:21.68,1:14:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道自己想做什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:24.31,1:14:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能够自我思考、拥有心灵这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:28.22,1:14:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是玛吉虚构出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:30.25,1:14:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是为了实现自己的愿望而活动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:35.92,1:14:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想见他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:38.46,1:14:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想看他高兴的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:42.20,1:14:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他勇很快就会到来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:46.43,1:14:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我已经不需要你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:52.81,1:14:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:28.58,1:15:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反应挺快的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:30.41,1:15:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正我们也耍不了小花招
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:32.91,1:15:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有强行突破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:35.08,1:15:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炸毁卫星轨道上的自动防卫卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:38.55,1:15:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁它们的碎片冲入大气层燃烧起来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:41.16,1:15:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们就混到那些碎片里 冲进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:45.23,1:15:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时候为了不被识别出机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:47.63,1:15:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要把操纵系统关掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:50.53,1:15:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我的程序计算出来的最佳方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:55.24,1:15:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然计算出来了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:56.80,1:15:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信你的计算
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:58.97,1:15:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:00.47,1:16:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,信任我的技术吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:02.48,1:16:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这时候与技术无关吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:04.48,1:16:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,几乎是全靠运气的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:07.01,1:16:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,运气也是技术的一部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:10.48,1:16:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就更加没法信任你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:55.79,1:17:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太美了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:59.09,1:18:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太美了 莎朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:02.00,1:18:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来 用那光辉照耀未来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:49.54,1:18:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还不如让我飞过去比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:54.48,1:18:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也曾任性的偷走过机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:57.22,1:19:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,长官们为了帮我掩盖证据费了很大力气
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:01.99,1:19:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来这次轮到我帮别人来掩盖证据了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:04.99,1:19:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:08.70,1:19:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尽情地去飞翔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:23.21,1:19:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来能赶的上约会时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:42.46,1:19:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伽尔德
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:43.80,1:19:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:45.20,1:19:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:46.33,1:19:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本应该由你变成灰烬的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:48.97,1:19:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼 阴险的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:51.00,1:19:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总是在别人背后打转
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:03.55,1:20:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没时间陪你这个白痴玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:25.44,1:20:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你总是要妨碍我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:32.44,1:20:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:58.94,1:20:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从小时候起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:00.31,1:21:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就总是跟在我后面打转
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:03.38,1:21:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人的屁股你也穷追不舍
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:05.78,1:21:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:06.98,1:21:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,元旦那天的“懦夫博弈”也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:06.98,1:21:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【chicken race】：一种游戏，也被称作斗鸡博弈（chicken game）
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:09.28,1:21:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明是我赢了 你还要胡搅蛮缠
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:12.79,1:21:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你的脚先往后退的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:16.66,1:21:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想翻旧帐吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:21.16,1:21:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的“GUNS”CDV车
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:21.16,1:21:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20}{\an8}【CDV】：微型厢式车的简称
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:23.86,1:21:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到现在还没有还给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:30.17,1:21:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是你自己七年前随便弄丢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:35.68,1:21:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高中时我还请了你两次午饭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:43.68,1:21:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我请了你十三次
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:46.72,1:21:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你算的很清楚嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:28.33,1:22:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学院祭的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:29.86,1:22:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毁掉我飞机的肯定也是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:33.03,1:22:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鬼才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:35.43,1:22:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别装傻
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:39.34,1:22:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这家伙真可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:09.44,1:23:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:12.37,1:23:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不管什么时候\N都要毁掉我重要的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:19.65,1:23:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:20.61,1:23:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把我重要的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:24.55,1:23:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啰嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:41.03,1:23:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,七年前那个时候也是一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:46.01,1:23:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不是你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:54.35,1:23:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果不是你在那里的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:01.48,1:25:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错 是我做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:04.62,1:25:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把一切都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:09.26,1:25:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之后我把自己的记忆锁了起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:15.20,1:25:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我失去他了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:19.70,1:25:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为恢复真正记忆的代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:24.90,1:25:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我坏掉了吗…疯了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:49.53,1:25:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来你没事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:52.93,1:25:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然的咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:59.44,1:26:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别太当真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:01.91,1:26:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小时候我们不是经常玩人力飞机吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:05.55,1:26:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关掉引擎 随风翱翔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:11.02,1:26:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我管这叫做“必杀龙鸟猛袭”
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:39.21,1:26:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你应该知道以前的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:45.05,1:26:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道又怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:47.32,1:26:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一直被我骂成是叛徒、卑鄙小人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:53.49,1:26:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谬她也知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:57.83,1:27:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们可怜我这个杰特拉帝人 故意瞒着我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:01.50,1:27:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上中学的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:04.90,1:27:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我毁掉了你制作的飞机
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:08.48,1:27:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:09.71,1:27:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为它做的很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:11.64,1:27:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想试飞一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:13.75,1:27:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:16.52,1:27:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把过去的事都忘掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:23.89,1:27:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:28.19,1:27:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你肯定还有瞒着我的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:30.30,1:27:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:54.39,1:27:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到头来 他们还是很要好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:06.70,1:28:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歌声
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:12.41,1:28:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:17.41,1:28:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GHOST吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:19.05,1:28:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于碰到它了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:20.98,1:28:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醒过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:24.22,1:28:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伽尔德
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:25.08,1:28:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我的约会对象 你别出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:27.85,1:28:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我的台词
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:29.62,1:28:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歌声难道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:58.49,1:28:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是莎朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:00.92,1:29:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她连MACROSS号的主电脑都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:03.99,1:29:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇 我在等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:08.50,1:29:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:10.80,1:29:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这东西在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:13.13,1:29:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她完全失控了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:15.13,1:29:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GHOST也被莎朗控制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:17.67,1:29:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:18.74,1:29:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在等你 勇
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:21.01,1:29:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只等你一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:22.64,1:29:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谬…谬呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:24.78,1:29:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她只是一个空壳
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:26.65,1:29:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把歌唱和爱情都交托给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:30.38,1:29:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她脑内只剩下一片空白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:32.15,1:29:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:33.15,1:29:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你做了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:34.65,1:29:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你对谬怎么样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:39.43,1:29:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你们 请救救我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:54.54,1:29:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经没人能分开我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:58.28,1:29:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:00.05,1:30:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:00.88,1:30:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:01.92,1:30:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怪物由我来对付
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:03.58,1:30:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去谬那里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:05.55,1:30:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伽尔德
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:20.00,1:30:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不论何时都要保护谬
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:21.83,1:30:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我们的誓言吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:28.43,1:30:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勇
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:00.71,1:31:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谬在等着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:03.11,1:31:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧 你一定要把她抢回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:08.28,1:31:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正你也赢不了GHOST
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:10.48,1:31:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:11.42,1:31:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样做或许更明智
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:13.62,1:31:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连你也这样说？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:15.96,1:31:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别慢吞吞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:20.39,1:31:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真气人 一个个的都这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:25.13,1:31:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之后可别哭着求我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:57.39,1:32:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发生什么事情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:59.39,1:33:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MACROSS在动
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:19.91,1:33:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像记起来了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:25.55,1:33:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,继续接近有危险 可能是陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:28.25,1:33:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,闭嘴 正合我意
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:36.13,1:33:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗、受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:40.50,1:33:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我继承了你内心深处的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:46.54,1:33:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你收藏起来的一切感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:05.86,1:34:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发生什么事了
